  "description": "Adds boost blocks to PocketMine-MP.",
  "readme_markdown": "<h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-boostblock\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#boostblock\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>BoostBlock</h1>\n<p>Adds boost blocks to PocketMine-MP.</p>\n<p>These boost blocks can be defined to a block or a position.</p>\n<p>You can configure the boost amount in the config.yml.</p>\n<h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-command\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#command\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Command</h1>\n<p>/boostblock - Manage boost blocks with a single command!</p>\n<h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-api\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#api\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>API</h1>\n<p>use OguzhanUmutlu\\BoostBlock\\BoostBlock;</p>\n<p>BoostBlock::setBoostBlock($player, new AngryVillagerParticle($player));</p>\n<p>BoostBlock::unsetBoostBlock($player);</p>\n<script defer src=\"https://static.cloudflareinsights.com/beacon.min.js/v8c78df7c7c0f484497ecbca7046644da1771523124516\" integrity=\"sha512-8DS7rgIrAmghBFwoOTujcf6D9rXvH8xm8JQ1Ja01h9QX8EzXldiszufYa4IFfKdLUKTTrnSFXLDkUEOTrZQ8Qg==\" data-cf-beacon='{\"version\":\"2024.11.0\",\"token\":\"508eb1d242ef46b690a0886422106e77\",\"r\":1,\"server_timing\":{\"name\":{\"cfCacheStatus\":true,\"cfEdge\":true,\"cfExtPri\":true,\"cfL4\":true,\"cfOrigin\":true,\"cfSpeedBrain\":true},\"location_startswith\":null}}' crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>",
